"{\"uid\": \"wnd.com-2024-08-no-scientific-way-to-differentiate-between-men-and-women-olympics-official-claims\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByOwen Klinsky, Daily Caller News Foundation  August 10, 2024      International Olympic Committee (IOC) President Thomas Bach suggested there is no scientific way to differentiate between men and women during a press conference on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daily Caller\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\"}, {\"begin\": 67, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 115, \"end\": 126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sex eligibility rules have been a point ofcontentionat the 2024 Paris Olympics, with Italian boxer Angela Carini withdrawing just 46 seconds into her fight with Algerian fighter Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9970764425715646, \"rank\": 0.002197336939743502, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 340, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103662667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9796935097848046, \"rank\": 0.020683411301587153, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps as a result, Bach was asked Friday if the committee would perform a review of its sex change guidelines, in response to which he stated there was no concrete, scientific way to differentiate men from women.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.999997185203352, \"rank\": 2.814804588835453e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have said from the very beginning, if somebody presented us [a] scientifically solid system how to identify men and women we [the IOC] are the first ones to do it,\\\" Bach told reporters.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.324480069343089e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.999997185203352, \"rank\": 2.814804588835453e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not as easy as some in this cultural world may want to portray it - that the XX or the XY [chromosome] is the clear distinction between men and women.\\\"\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999404690261, \"rank\": 5.953108513217517e-08, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"score\": 0.5548491819416891, \"rank\": 0.8022913035407603, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WATCH:    Strap a dunce cap on this guy and give him the old point and laughhttps://t.co/7AA0jj59ca  - Vince Coglianese (@VinceCoglianese)August 9, 2024    As of now, testosterone level - not whether someone has an XX or XY chromosomal pattern - is the key criterion in Olympic eligibility, NBC Newsreported.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"t.co\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999404690261, \"rank\": 5.953108513217517e-08, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"score\": 0.5548491819416891, \"rank\": 0.8022913035407603, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get the hottest, most important news stories on the Internet - delivered FREE to your inbox as soon as they break!\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take just 30 seconds and sign up for WND's Email News Alerts!\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WND\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach also suggested climate change could affect the timing of future Olympics during the Friday press conference,accordingto Sports Illustrated (SI).\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.999997185203352, \"rank\": 2.814804588835453e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the climate change is continuing in a way that the experts are forecasting it, then it will be very difficult to organize Olympic Games in summer, in August,\\\" Bach said, according to SI.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1801, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.999997185203352, \"rank\": 2.814804588835453e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC president's comments come after the 2024 Paris Olympics opening ceremony starred drag queensposingas Christian imagery, including \\\"The Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.324480069343089e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1939, \"end\": 1948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.7161032115098771, \"rank\": 0.3924479966617353, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This story originally was published bythe Daily Caller News Foundation.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daily Caller\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\"}]}, {\"sentence\"